data.description: OVERSIZED .28 ACRE CITY WATER LOT with the desirable pie shape enabling you to have a bigger than normal backyard. PLENTY of room on the sides to park your boat, RV or other toys! Well maintained, meticulously clean, & move-in ready CONCRETE BLOCK, 4 bedroom, 2 bath home with a NEWER ROOF (9/2018), A/C (10/2018), WATER HEATER (1/2023) and IMPACT FRONT DOOR & WINDOWS (8/2020). A gorgeous open floorplan kitchen with granite countertops and stainless appliances opens to the family and dining rooms so you'll be at the center of it all while entertaining friends or just relaxing with family. OVERSIZED MASTER BEDROOM. MASSIVE 20' x 56' PAVER PATIO in the oversized backyard allows for peaceful evenings entertaining friends & family or simply taking a tranquil mid-afternoon siesta to catch up on much needed rest....AND NO HOA RESTRICTIONS TO TELL YOU WHAT YOU CAN AND CAN'T DO....Come take a look for yourself!
